---
title: Double Lamb Rump & Roast Veggie Salad with Indian Coconut Sauce
description: It's roast lamb, but not as you know it! We're using our mild yet flavourful North Indian spice blend to lift succulent lamb rump to new heights. With a generous helping of roasted veggies, It's all you need to create a meal fit for royalty!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67c0f6f160686822766eb41b-9bc24cf4-dcbc43e4.jpeg
